<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 06:21:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>HEDGEFLOW 美国对冲基金涌入中国京东、GDS：高盛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hedgeflow-us-hedge-funds-pile-into-chinas-jdcom-gds-goldman-2024-11-21/</link><description>路透社查阅的高盛报告显示，美国对冲基金第三季度加大了对在美上市中国公司的投资，其中电子商务零售商京东和数据中心运营商万国数据控股公司领投。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 06:08:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hedgeflow-us-hedge-funds-pile-into-chinas-jdcom-gds-goldman-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>ACEA 称 10 月份欧洲汽车销量持平，电动汽车取得进展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-car-sales-flat-october-evs-gain-ground-acea-says-2024-11-21/</link><description>周四的行业数据显示，欧洲十月份新车销量在连续两个月下降后持平，而向纯电动或混合动力车型的过渡在本月取得了进展。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 05:07:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-car-sales-flat-october-evs-gain-ground-acea-says-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>集装箱托运人通过双燃料船订单对冲绿色转型</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/container-shippers-hedging-green-transition-with-dual-fuel-vessel-orders-2024-11-21/</link><description>如果绿色燃料成本太高，混合动力发动机允许运营商转向石油。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 05:05:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/container-shippers-hedging-green-transition-with-dual-fuel-vessel-orders-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，星巴克考虑出售中国业务的股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-considers-selling-stake-chinese-business-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-11-21/</link><description>彭博社周三援引知情人士的话报道称，星巴克正在探索其中国业务的选择，包括将业务股份出售给当地合作伙伴的可能性。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 04:44:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-considers-selling-stake-chinese-business-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国顾问呼吁稳定2025年5%经济增长目标，加大刺激力度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-advisers-call-steady-5-2025-economic-growth-goal-stronger-stimulus-2024-11-21/</link><description>中国政府顾问建议北京维持明年5.0%左右的经济增长目标，推动采取更强有力的财政刺激措施，以减轻美国预期上调关税对中国出口的影响。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 04:14:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-advisers-call-steady-5-2025-economic-growth-goal-stronger-stimulus-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普任命卢特尼克领导美国贸易和关税后，他的对华关系受到批评</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/lutnicks-china-ties-draw-fire-after-trump-taps-him-lead-us-trade-tariffs-2024-11-21/</link><description>周三，在共和党候任总统唐纳德·特朗普任命投资银行家霍华德·卢特尼克（Howard Lutnick）领导已成为美中贸易战矛头的机构后，他对中国的敞口急剧缓解。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 03:58:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/lutnicks-china-ties-draw-fire-after-trump-taps-him-lead-us-trade-tariffs-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>由于英伟达的预测令人失望，亚洲股市表现不佳</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-21/</link><description>亚洲股市周四下跌，此前人工智能宠儿英伟达的收入增长放缓令投资者失望，而美元坚挺，比特币创下历史新高，受到对美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普政策希望的提振。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 03:03:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：英伟达击败，但未能提供火花</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-11-20/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 21:48:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国国防部长拒绝与五角大楼负责人会面</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-defense-minister-declines-meeting-with-pentagon-chief-2024-11-20/</link><description>中国国防部长在老挝举行的国防领导人会议期间拒绝与美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀会面，五角大楼负责人周三表示，此举是不幸的。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 18:32:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-defense-minister-declines-meeting-with-pentagon-chief-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>法国马克龙敦促习近平取消对中国干邑白兰地的关税，轩尼诗工人罢工</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hennessy-workers-strike-frances-macron-urges-xi-drop-china-cognac-tariffs-2024-11-20/</link><description>在法国总统马克龙敦促中国国家主席习近平取消关税后，轩尼诗员工周三延长罢工，抗议轩尼诗计划在中国装瓶干邑以规避进口关税。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 16:43:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hennessy-workers-strike-frances-macron-urges-xi-drop-china-cognac-tariffs-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>首席执行官表示，意法半导体与华虹合作是因为芯片制造商需要中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/stmicro-partners-with-hua-hong-chipmakers-need-china-says-ceo-2024-11-20/</link><description>欧洲计算机芯片制造商意法半导体首席执行官周三宣布了与中国晶圆代工厂华虹合作的新计划，他认为在中国进行本地制造对其竞争地位至关重要。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 16:33:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/stmicro-partners-with-hua-hong-chipmakers-need-china-says-ceo-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国生物科技公司来凯医药与礼来公司合作开发保肌减肥药</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/china-based-biotech-laekna-teams-up-with-lilly-develop-muscle-preserving-obesity-2024-11-20/</link><description>生物技术公司周三表示，礼来公司和香港上市公司来凯医药将合作开发一种实验性肥胖药物，旨在帮助患者减肥同时保留肌肉。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 15:11:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/china-based-biotech-laekna-teams-up-with-lilly-develop-muscle-preserving-obesity-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>国际原子能机构格罗西希望伊朗限制高浓缩铀库存</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iaeas-grossi-hopes-irans-capping-highly-enriched-uranium-stock-holds-2024-11-20/</link><description>联合国核监察机构负责人拉斐尔·格罗西周三表示，他希望伊朗将铀库存限制在略低于武器级的水平的举措能够持续下去，因为该机构的董事会将通过一项西方起草的决议，该决议可能会破坏这一计划。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 14:01:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iaeas-grossi-hopes-irans-capping-highly-enriched-uranium-stock-holds-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>福特将在欧洲裁员以应对电动汽车转型，中国竞争对手遭受损失</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ford-cut-14-european-jobs-blaming-ev-shift-rising-competition-2024-11-20/</link><description>福特周三表示，将裁员约 14% 的欧洲员工，并将近年来的亏损归咎于电动汽车需求疲软、政府对电动汽车转型的支持不力以及来自受补贴的中国竞争对手的竞争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 13:32:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ford-cut-14-european-jobs-blaming-ev-shift-rising-competition-2024-11-20/</guid></item><item><title>由于担心特朗普可能征收关税，券商认为 2025 年“不确定”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/brokerages-see-uncertain-2025-worries-over-potential-trump-tariffs-2024-11-20/</link><description>各大券商表示，美国政策的不确定性可能会在 2025 年小幅放缓全球经济增长。他们预计，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普提议的关税将加剧全球市场的波动，引发通胀压力，进而限制主要央行放松货币政策的范围。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 13:02:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/brokerages-see-uncertain-2025-worries-over-potential-trump-tariffs-2024-11-20/</guid></item></channel></rss>